><p class="description"><s>Cells are Gram-negative, aerobic rods.</s><s>Motile with a single polar flagellum.</s><s>Catalase- and oxidase-positive.</s><s>Nitrates are reduced to nitrites.</s><s>NaCl is not needed for growth.</s><s>Predominant fatty acids include C<sub>17 : 1</sub>ω8<em>c</em>, summed feature 3 (C<sub>16 : 1</sub>ω7<em>c</em> and/or iso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub> 2-OH) and C<sub>17 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The genus belongs phylogenetically to the class <em>Gammaproteobacteria</em>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Zhongshania antarctica</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>